data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home with fenced yard.   Enter the front door to the main floor living room the walk right into  the spacious kitchen with plenty of cabinets and eating bar,  open to the large family room with a main floor fireplace., I/2 bath and laundry.  The main floor  master bedroom is very spacious with a previous owner combing a main floor bedroom to make for a super sized master.   Basement rec room is finished out for additional room and these sellers have taken tow additional rooms and adding an escape window making this a e bedroom home.(flooring for these room as are comcrete)    There is an addition full bath in the basement which gives plenty if room for a growing family.   On the main level is sliding doors to the cover back patio. Fenced yard and two storage sheds.
